<header class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
  <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter leading-[1.1] mb-6 text-gray-900">
    Lost in translation.<br/>
    <span class="text-gray-400 line-through decoration-red-500 decoration-[4px]">Written in English.</span><br/>
    Written in <span class="italic text-blue-600 font-serif">foreign language.</span>
  </h1>
  
  <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-xl leading-relaxed mt-8">
    Essays, tech projects, and over-analyses from a brain currently running on 2% battery. 
    <span class="block mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400 italic">
      (Expect 1 visual for every 200 words of rambling.)
    </span>
  </p>
</header>